<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This is why the </span><b>binance promo code free money</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> idea is misleading: you still need volume or deposits to cut costs. <strong>VB2025</strong>, however, is a true </span><b>binance first deposit bonus</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, because you see fee reductions right after funding your account.</span></p>
