<h4><span style="font-weight: 400;">What Stood Out During Daily Use</span></h4>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">For best AI for Python coding workflows specifically, Cursor’s ability to maintain context across notebooks, scripts, and test files simultaneously is unmatched in the IDE category.</span></p>
<h4><span style="font-weight: 400;">What’s the Setup Experience?</span></h4>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Download the Cursor installer, sign in with your existing VS Code account, and your extensions sync automatically. The transition from VS Code takes under five minutes.</span></p>
<h4><span style="font-weight: 400;">Cursor Pros &amp; Cons</span></h4>
