<h4><span style="font-weight: 400;">Tabnine Pros &amp; Cons</span></h4>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Pros: Zero code retention, on-premise option, SOC 2, GDPR-compliant, competitive autocomplete, free tier available</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Cons: Less capable than Cursor for agentic tasks, smaller feature set than Copilot, premium features require enterprise plan</span></li>
</ul>
